# coding-agent/.cursorrules

## Project

This is an AI Coding Agent built with LangGraph, MCP, and FastAPI.
Target languages: Kotlin, Java, TypeScript, React, Android.

## Python style

- Always use type hints (Pydantic models for all API contracts)
- Prefer async/await throughout
- Use match/case for tool routing in MCP server
- FastAPI dependency injection over global state

## Architecture

- mcp-server/server.py: MCP tools (never import agent code here)
- agent/agent.py: LangGraph graph definition
- agent/api.py: FastAPI HTTP layer only, no business logic
- frontend/src/: React TypeScript

## LangGraph patterns

- AgentState is a TypedDict with Annotated fields
- All nodes are pure functions: (state) -> partial state update
- Tools come from MCP via langchain-mcp-adapters

## Never

- No synchronous file I/O in async functions
- No hardcoded API keys
- No business logic in api.py
